query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-layout',
'async-await',
'compiler-construction',
'conditional-statements',
'gdb',
'geolocation',
'glsl',
'homebrew',
'jar',
'logstash',
'mocking',
'multidimensional-array',
'svg',
'vagrant',
'winforms');
